videos.description: Mike Conley gets the inbound pass and knocks down a long range jump shot to beat the buzzer at the end of the first quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Conley sinks buzzer-beater to end the 1st quarter) 2021/06/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Conley sinks buzzer-beater to end the 1st quarter

videos.description: Donovan Mitchell elevates and fades to his right as he drains a 3 to beat the halftime buzzer and give the Jazz a 75-51 lead over the Grizzlies.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Mitchell knocks down fadeaway 3 to end first half) 2021/06/03

videos.headline: Mitchell knocks down fadeaway 3 to end first half

videos.description: Donovan Mitchell puts up 30 points and 10 assists as he leads the Jazz to eliminate the Grizzlies from the postseason with a 126-110 win in Game 5.
